About our team.

We are an innovative team dedicated to transforming the online gaming experience through blockchain technology. Our project combines the thrill of poker with the security and transparency of blockchain, creating a revolutionary platform for players worldwide.

Job Summary:
We are seeking a talented and motivated Web3 Full Stack Developer to join our team. The ideal candidate will have a strong background in backend development using Node.js and Express.js, as well as frontend development with React. You will be responsible for integrating blockchain wallets, managing user assets, and enhancing the gameplay experience with animations and security measures.

Key Responsibilities:
- Develop and maintain the backend using Node.js and Express.js.
- Build responsive and dynamic user interfaces with React.
- Integrate blockchain wallet solutions for seamless user access and asset management.
- Implement animations and visual effects to enhance the gaming experience.
- Ensure the security and integrity of smart contracts and user data.
- Collaborate with designers, product managers, and other developers to create engaging gameplay features.

Qualifications:
- Proven experience as a full stack developer with expertise in Node.js, Express.js, and React.
- Familiarity with web3 and smart contract development (Ethereum, Solidity, etc.).
- Strong understanding of wallet integrations (MetaMask, WalletConnect, etc.).
- Experience with database management (MongoDB, PostgreSQL, etc.).
- Knowledge of security best practices in blockchain and web development.
- Ability to create and implement engaging animations in web applications.
- Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail.
- Strong communication and teamwork abilities.

What We Offer:
- Competitive salary and benefits.
- Flexible working environment.
- Opportunity to work on cutting-edge technology in the gaming industry.
- A supportive and creative team atmosphere.

